Package net.minecraftforge.client.model

Klasse CompositeModel

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.client.model.CompositeModel
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
IUnbakedGeometry<CompositeModel>
public class CompositeModel extends Object implements IUnbakedGeometry<CompositeModel>
A model composed of several named children.

These respect component visibility as specified in IGeometryBakingContext and can additionally be provided with an item-specific render ordering, for multi-pass arrangements.
